Arcane Tracker is an automatic deck tracker for Hearthstone.

• <b>100% automatic</b>. No manual input needed.
• See the cards you have played and the ones that remain in your deck in an overlay.
• HSReplay.net integration.
• Track-o-bot integration.
• Secret detector.
• Zero configuration: just launch the game from the Arcane Tracker launcher.
• Works for both ranked games and arena.

Join us on reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/arcanetracker/
